The data has recently been made available to the public for free!!


Requirements:
-Microsoft Flight Simulator X (FSX)

Should be enjoyed with:
-Airports of Norway
-Norway Scenic X 
-Norway Bridges X 

Package contains:
-Mesh for Norway. max resolution is LOD12 (9.5 meters). 
-The number of *.bgl files in the scenery folder is 61
-Files are named by their North-West corner, ie N635E115 - North 63.5 deg East 11.5 deg
-Most files cover an area of 1 deg latitude and 2 deg longitude
-Each area file has all LOD levels from LOD0-LOD12 embedded. 


Installation:

- Unzip to folder of your choice. e.g FSXAddon scenery. Remember to use 
 folder names when unzipping!. (the BGL files should reside in "Norway10m_meshScenery"

- Add this scenery in the FSX scenery library (Settings/Scenery Library)
